      "message": "LGTM, just one additional general question:\n\nDo you want to allow for overlap between the syzkaller and syzcorpus test suites?\n\nIf not, we may want to look into how to enforce the attributes to be mutually exclusive or at least document it somewhere.\n\nThis can be addressed in a separate CL though and is a small concern given that I don\u0027t imagine other\u0027s using this attribute in the near future.",
